# 6. Business Rules

## BR-01

Every lead must be assigned to an owner.

## BR-02

Mandatory customer information must be validated before lead creation.

## BR-03

Only qualified leads can be converted into opportunities.

## BR-04

Every active lead must have an associated follow-up task.

## BR-05

Duplicate records must be flagged before creation.

## BR-06

Lead assignment must occur within one minute of lead creation.

## BR-07

Test drive confirmation notifications must be sent automatically.

